  EffectDiscription_ENG: While you have a [Nene Amano] in play, you may use this
    card without meeting its color requirements.[Main] Trash 3 cards from the top
    of your deck. Then, you may play 1 [DarkKnightmon] from your trash for its memory
    cost. If you play a Digimon card with DigiXros requirements by this effect, you
    may also place cards from your trash in digivolution cards for a DigiXros.
